  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate 13 C Isotope Ratio Measurement for Urea Cycle Capacity Assessment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Feasibility Study in Healthy Subjects and Healthy Asymptomatic Subjects Genetically Disposed to Urea Cycle Disorders to Evaluate the Use of 13 C Isotope Ratio Measurement</official_title>
